    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      World news story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Information and events for British citizens in Hungary
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The British Embassy and consulates have been holding a series of meetings to inform British citizens working and living in Hungary about their rights after the 31 January 2020. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 28 December 2018
    <br></br>Last updated 16 November 2020
      — <a href="#history" class="app-c-published-dates__history-link govuk-link">see all updates</a>
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
        <dl data-module="track-click">
            <dt class="app-c-publisher-metadata__term">
              From:
            </dt>
            <dd class="app-c-publisher-metadata__definition" data-module="gem-toggle">
                <span class="app-c-publisher-metadata__definition-sentence">
                  <a class="govuk-link" href="/world/organisations/british-embassy-budapest">British Embassy Budapest</a>
                </span>
            </dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
  </div>

    </div>
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds content-bottom-margin">
    <div class="responsive-bottom-margin">
      <figure class="app-c-figure" lang="en">
  <img class="app-c-figure__image" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/image_data/file/94874/s300_citizens_outreach.jpg" alt="Information for British citizens in Hungary"></img>
    <figcaption class="app-c-figure__figcaption">

    </figcaption>
</figure>

      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>In our network’s continuous effort to reach as many British nationals in Hungary as possible, we are announcing further events. This is your opportunity to ask the questions that concern you.</p>

<p>The meetings are free and open to all interested British nationals.</p>

<h2 id="upcoming-events-in-hungary">Upcoming events in Hungary</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th scope="col">Date</th>
      <th scope="col">Event</th>
      <th scope="col">Details</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Thursday 19 November, 5.00pm - 6.30pm</td>
      <td>online event</td>
      <td>The event is free of charge</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>To receive updates on outreach events in your area, <a rel="external" href="https://www.facebook.com/ukinhungary/" class="govuk-link">follow us on Facebook</a> and on <a rel="external" href="https://twitter.com/ukinhungary" class="govuk-link">Twitter</a> and keep an eye on this website for more news.</p>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Visit our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/living-in-hungary" class="govuk-link">Living in Hungary guide</a> for practical information. You can also <a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/world/living-in-hungary" class="govuk-link">sign up for email alerts</a> when the guide is updated.</p>
</div>

<h2 id="past-events-in-hungary">Past events in Hungary</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Budapest: 24 September 2019</li>
  <li>Balatonújlak: 22 August 2019</li>
  <li>Budapest: 20 March 2019</li>
  <li>Budapest: 9 January 2019, please  find the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/speeches/townhall-meeting-for-british-nationals-opening-remarks" class="govuk-link">transcript of the opening remarks here</a>
</li>
  <li>Budapest: 22 January 2018</li>
</ul>
</div>

